Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.45,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，你今晚能顾孩子吗？\N{\ren}Jerry, can you watch the kids tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:11.70,zh,,0,0,0,,有人在赛马场播贝瑞怀特的歌\N{\ren}Someone played Barry White over the racetrack speakers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.75,zh,,0,0,0,,－所以有七只马怀孕　－我…\N{\ren}- and now there's a seven-horse pregnancy. - Oh, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:16.21,zh,,0,0,0,,他不能顾孩子，今天是男士之夜\N{\ren}No, he can't watch the kids, it's guys' night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.01,zh,,0,0,0,,你们什么时候开始会一起玩了？\N{\ren}How did you two start having guys' nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.47,zh,,0,0,0,,你不满意我喜欢你的蠢老公吗？\N{\ren}So now, you're complaining that I like your stupid husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:22.64,zh,,0,0,0,,不是，我希望你喜欢我的蠢老公\N{\ren}No, I want you to like my stupid husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:25.86,zh,,0,0,0,,周五夜就是瑞克和杰瑞男士之夜\N{\ren}Well, then accept that Friday nights are all about Rick and Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:27.61,zh,,0,0,0,,－我们是好兄弟　－好喔\N{\ren}- We're buds! - Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:30.24,zh,,0,0,0,,我没时间消化这件事\N{\ren}I don't nearly have the time to unpack this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.00,zh,,0,0,0,,桑美，你今天负责看好弟弟\N{\ren}Summer, you're in charge of your brother tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:34.29,zh,,0,0,0,,不能开派对和吸电子烟之类的\N{\ren}No parties and no vape... stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:36.38,zh,,0,0,0,,妈，我邀了朋友来\N{\ren}Mom, I have a friend coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:37.51,zh,,0,0,0,,－可以吗？　－不公平\N{\ren}- Is that cool? - No fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:39.76,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，我才刚说不让姐姐办派对\N{\ren}No fair, Morty. I just told your sister no parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:41.39,zh,,0,0,0,,－才一个人而已　－那也算派对\N{\ren}- It's one friend. - That's a party, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.10,zh,,0,0,0,,不过是布鲁斯恰贝\N{\ren}But it's Bruce Chutback!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:44.94,zh,,0,0,0,,什么？妈，就让莫蒂邀朋友来吧\N{\ren}Wait, what? Mom, let Morty have one friend over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.44,zh,,0,0,0,,拜托，这里又不是中国\N{\ren}For God's sake this isn't China.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:47.86,zh,,0,0,0,,都着冠了，我得走了\N{\ren}And they're all crowning. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.53,zh,,0,0,0,,我选择信任和尊重你们\N{\ren}I am giving you two trust and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:51.29,zh,,0,0,0,,你们如果搞砸，把家传送到远方\N{\ren}So if you mess up and teleport this house
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:53.75,zh,,0,0,0,,你们最好就待着，别回来了\N{\ren}then it'd be wise to stay on it and not come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.92,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，你们碰我的东西就死定了\N{\ren}I'm with her. Touch my shit and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:00.81,zh,,0,0,0,,新来的转学生布鲁斯恰贝要来？\N{\ren}New transfer student Bruce Chutback is coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:02.77,zh,,0,0,0,,－你怎么邀到的？　－我们同班\N{\ren}- How'd you lock that down? - He's in my math class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:05.40,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是随口问问就邀到了\N{\ren}I don't know, I just kinda shot my shot and it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.53,zh,,0,0,0,,应该是因为他是新生\N{\ren}I guess 'cause he's new.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.70,zh,,0,0,0,,－你竟然准备葡萄？　－我承认\N{\ren}- And you're putting out grapes? - Yeah, I'll admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:11.00,zh,,0,0,0,,－我应付不来　－你需要我帮忙\N{\ren}- I'm a little bit out of my depth. - You're gonna need my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.00,zh,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯迟早会发现\N{\ren}It's only a matter of time before Bruce learns
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.26,zh,,0,0,0,,你是个外公宝，常跟外星人乱搞\N{\ren}you're a creepy little Grandpa's boy, always climbing up into alien asses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:19.01,zh,,0,0,0,,或是你会用洗发精洗阴毛的传言\N{\ren}Or the Summer Smith shampoos her pubes rumor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:20.56,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，算你狠\N{\ren}OK. You came to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.77,zh,,0,0,0,,我们都得在恰贝发现我们很逊前\N{\ren}We need to acquire Chutback's loyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:24.19,zh,,0,0,0,,让他成为我们的朋友\N{\ren}before he finds out we're losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:26.61,zh,,0,0,0,,我们能运用的时间非常短\N{\ren}By all accounts, it's a very small window.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:29.91,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我们最好携手合作\N{\ren}So, I think it's in our best interest to work as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:31.75,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我们毕竟是一家人\N{\ren}Yeah. Most people would call that family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:35.25,zh,,0,0,0,,－你好恶　－你不喜欢就是仇女\N{\ren}- You're so gross! - You have to like it or you're sexist!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:39.68,zh,,0,0,0,,－我能转地狱方块吗？　－当然\N{\ren}- Can I do the hell cube this time? - Sure, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:43.81,zh,,0,0,0,,要怎样才算完成？\N{\ren}How do you know when it's aligned?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:45.44,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，它不过是邪恶方块\N{\ren}C'mon, Jerry, just... It's an evil cube.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.03,zh,,0,0,0,,只要摇一摇让它流血就好\N{\ren}Just shake it until it draws blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:55.21,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，你今天打扮得真好看\N{\ren}Jerry! Exquisite finery this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:59.26,zh,,0,0,0,,别跟罗斯说，这是大卖场买的\N{\ren}Well, don't tell Ross but I got this little ditty from Kohl's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.06,zh,,0,0,0,,我不懂，但太棒了\N{\ren}I love that I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.40,zh,,0,0,0,,你今天准备了什么有趣的行程？\N{\ren}Tell us, what delights have you in store for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.08,zh,,0,0,0,,你们一定会喜欢，是杰瑞OK\N{\ren}Oh, you'll love this. I call it Jerry-oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:09.24,zh,,0,0,0,,猜猜看是什么意思\N{\ren}I'll let you guess why.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:14.50,zh,,0,0,0,,怎么了，瑞克？玩得不开心吗？\N{\ren}What's the matter, Rick? Are you having a bad time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:16.09,zh,,0,0,0,,对我们来说，不开心…\N{\ren}Because to us, a bad time is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.43,zh,,0,0,0,,我知道，就是开心\N{\ren}Yeah, a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:19.60,zh,,0,0,0,,因为你们跟芝麻街的奥斯卡一样\N{\ren}Because you guys are like Oscar the fucking Grouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.52,zh,,0,0,0,,我们喜欢痛苦\N{\ren}We love suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:24.15,zh,,0,0,0,,所以才喜欢跟杰瑞一起玩\N{\ren}Therefore, we love hanging out with Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:26.61,zh,,0,0,0,,我们很喜欢他的逊\N{\ren}His lameness is our candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:28.99,zh,,0,0,0,,对，我懂，但这还要持续多久？\N{\ren}Yeah, I got that, but when is enough gonna be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:32.92,zh,,0,0,0,,你得为那些瑕疵皮钩付出代价\N{\ren}When we decide you've repaid your debt for those faulty skin hooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:34.21,zh,,0,0,0,,我们走运了，各位\N{\ren}Hey, we're in luck, gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.39,zh,,0,0,0,,这里有破嘴乐团的所有歌\N{\ren}They've got the entire Smash Mouth catalog!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.87,zh,,0,0,0,,不，莫蒂，等等\N{\ren}No! Morty. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.88,zh,,0,0,0,,*布鲁斯恰贝*\N{\ren}*Bruce Chutback!*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.64,zh,,0,0,0,,*新同学*\N{\ren}*Newest kid in school*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.01,zh,,0,0,0,,*刚转学过来*\N{\ren}*Just transferred in*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.48,zh,,0,0,0,,*还不知道任何糗事*\N{\ren}*Hasn't done anything embarrassing yet*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.15,zh,,0,0,0,,*无限可能*\N{\ren}*Unlimited potential*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.28,zh,,0,0,0,,*什么事都有可能*\N{\ren}*Anybody's guess*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.62,zh,,0,0,0,,*没信用最完美*\N{\ren}*No credit is perfect credit*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.12,zh,,0,0,0,,*恰贝最棒了*\N{\ren}*Chutback is the best!*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:34.46,zh,,0,0,0,,－布鲁斯，你好吗？　－你好\N{\ren}- Bruce! Hey, how's it hangin', my guy? - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:41.14,zh,,0,0,0,,我们家能看到各个维度的电视\N{\ren}Here's something kinda cool TV from every dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:43.73,zh,,0,0,0,,－好　－是我的科学家外公弄的\N{\ren}- Cool. - Grandpa made it. He's a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.15,zh,,0,0,0,,欢迎继续收看旱鸭子跳水比赛\N{\ren}And now back to Olympic Diving With Bad Swimmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.82,zh,,0,0,0,,他要跳了，姿势很完美\N{\ren}There he goes. Perfect dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.50,zh,,0,0,0,,泳技很烂\N{\ren}Terrible swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.93,zh,,0,0,0,,这是贪食蛇吗？ 它会一直变大\N{\ren}Is that classic Snake? Boy, that guy just keeps getting bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.35,zh,,0,0,0,,我是桑美史密斯，莫蒂的姐姐\N{\ren}Hi, Summer Smith, Morty's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.56,zh,,0,0,0,,想不想喝沙发葡萄酒？\N{\ren}Want some sofa wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.73,zh,,0,0,0,,已经放好几周了，应该很好喝\N{\ren}It's been stashed for weeks. Should be good tasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.86,zh,,0,0,0,,酷，但我比较喜欢低酒精气泡酒\N{\ren}Tight. I'm more of like a Hard Seltzer guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.37,zh,,0,0,0,,酷，非常酷，超级酷\N{\ren}Tight. Very tight, extremely tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:13.92,zh,,0,0,0,,－你来帮我倒气泡酒 －警广…\N{\ren}- Morty, help me with the Seltz? - Feel fear... feel fee...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.75,zh,,0,0,0,,尽管吃葡萄\N{\ren}Feel free to have some grapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.34,zh,,0,0,0,,老弟，那婊子非常谨慎\N{\ren}Dude. This bitch plays it close to the vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.30,zh,,0,0,0,,对，他很有概念\N{\ren}Yeah, he really knows what's for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.47,zh,,0,0,0,,我们的状况很危急\N{\ren}I mean, we're drowning out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.14,zh,,0,0,0,,要快点引起他的兴趣\N{\ren}We need to get interesting fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.36,zh,,0,0,0,,我们得拿瑞克的东西\N{\ren}We're touching Rick's stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.52,zh,,0,0,0,,桑美，他说不行\N{\ren}Summer, he said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.78,zh,,0,0,0,,想得美，我说过别碰我的东西\N{\ren}Nah-uh-uh! I said, don't touch my shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.37,zh,,0,0,0,,我刚看了《侏罗纪公园》，真赞\N{\ren}Also, I just watched Jurassic Park on cable. So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.87,zh,,0,0,0,,说真的，如果碰我的东西\N{\ren}Seriously though,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.34,zh,,0,0,0,,我就把你的鸡鸡装进琥珀里\N{\ren}touch my shit and I'll freeze your dick in amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.38,zh,,0,0,0,,他走了，王八蛋，我们搞砸了\N{\ren}He left! Son of a bitch, we blew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.64,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我只是想再看一眼这辆车\N{\ren}Sorry. I just needed to get another look at this beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.60,zh,,0,0,0,,很像垃圾做成的太空船\N{\ren}Looks like a spaceship made of garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:44.77,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，布鲁斯\N{\ren}You called it, Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.65,zh,,0,0,0,,这辆车很酷，你们能开吗？\N{\ren}It's a pretty cool car. Can you guys drive it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.53,zh,,0,0,0,,－可以　－可以，但是我们…\N{\ren}- Yes. - Yes. We just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:49.99,zh,,0,0,0,,－需要　－拿钥匙\N{\ren}- Need. - To get the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.83,zh,,0,0,0,,我去拿，你们先聊\N{\ren}Which I am, you guys hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.17,zh,,0,0,0,,不聊也可以，我不是聊天希特勒\N{\ren}Or don't, I'm not a hang-out Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.80,zh,,0,0,0,,－今晚真酷　－是吗？\N{\ren}- Cool night. - Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.72,zh,,0,0,0,,我也不确定，夜晚嘛\N{\ren}I don't know. Nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.89,zh,,0,0,0,,差不多就这样，至于今晚\N{\ren}I mean, for what they are, this one, in my opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.48,zh,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该有8分？\N{\ren}I think it's an eight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.53,zh,,0,0,0,,满分16分，算普通\N{\ren}On a scale of 16. So... average?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:09.28,zh,,0,0,0,,－我他妈快挂了　－什么？\N{\ren}- Jesus Christ, I'm fucking dying up here. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:12.75,zh,,0,0,0,,拿到钥匙了，我们上车吧\N{\ren}Keys! So, uh... let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.88,zh,,0,0,0,,你不是瑞克\N{\ren}You are not Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.47,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，车，我是桑美，记得吗？\N{\ren}That's correct, Car. it's me Summer, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.97,zh,,0,0,0,,保护桑美？好朋友？\N{\ren}Keep Summer Safe? Buds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.35,zh,,0,0,0,,我知道你的存在\N{\ren}I am aware of your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.24,zh,,0,0,0,,－我来，关闭防御系统　－好喔\N{\ren}- I got this. Defense System offline. - Um, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.29,zh,,0,0,0,,只要有人叫我关闭就关闭\N{\ren}I'll just go offline whenever anyone suggests it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:32.75,zh,,0,0,0,,那我这防御系统也太烂了\N{\ren}That would make me the greatest defense system in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.84,zh,,0,0,0,,那要怎么关闭防御系统？\N{\ren}Well, how do you go offline?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:38.47,zh,,0,0,0,,我只会听从瑞克的指令\N{\ren}The answer to how I do anything, is Rick tells me.
